message.en_US: Wish me luck, Lea!
Lea!
Alright, it's time for our rematch after what happened in Satoshi's lab.
You think this is going to end any different?
I don't really care what the outcome is.
In truth, fighting against my equal is just too much fun!
I can certainly agree with that!
Gyahaha! Score one for me!
It's just one point. You still have four to go.
Ok, that was pretty good. I'll give you that.
And another point for me!
I've got to get it together.
As capable as ever, I see!
Ha! I've been wanting to get you with that!
I've really got to step up my game.
Only one more to go!
Looks like it's a win for us mortals.
At least until we have a rematch!
Looks like I win!
Just you wait until our next rematch, you'll see!
